---

<section id="challenges" class="py-24 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">
        Research Challenges
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Virtual Community introduces groundbreaking challenges that push the boundaries of multi-agent embodied AI research
      </p>
    </div>
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
      <!-- Community Planning Challenge -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-slate-100 border border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center mr-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-slate-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 20l-5.447-2.724A1 1 0 013 16.382V5.618a1 1 0 011.447-.894L9 7m0 13l6-3m-6 3V7m6 10l4.553 2.276A1 1 0 0021 18.382V7.618a1 1 0 00-1.447-.894L15 4m0 13V4m-6 3l6-3"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Community Planning</h3>
            <div class="text-slate-600 text-sm font-semibold">Multi-Agent Task Planning in Open Worlds</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          A groundbreaking challenge introducing multi-agent task planning in expansive open-world environments 
          where agents must coordinate across diverse indoor and outdoor scenes.
        </p>
          <div class="space-y-6">
          <!-- Assistant Tasks -->
          <div class="bg-slate-50 p-4 border border-slate-200">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-slate-100 border border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Assistant Tasks</h4>
            </div>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-3">
              Agents interact with humans and other agents to provide assistance in daily open-world activities.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-slate-200 text-slate-700 text-xs border border-slate-300">Human-Agent Interaction</span>
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-slate-200 text-slate-700 text-xs border border-slate-300">Daily Activities</span>
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-slate-200 text-slate-700 text-xs border border-slate-300">Real-world Context</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Campaign Tasks -->
          <div class="bg-slate-50 p-4 border border-slate-200">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-slate-100 border border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Campaign Tasks</h4>
            </div>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-3">
              Agents must efficiently explore the community and connect with one another to achieve collective goals.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-slate-200 text-slate-700 text-xs border border-slate-300">Community Exploration</span>
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-slate-200 text-slate-700 text-xs border border-slate-300">Agent Networking</span>
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-slate-200 text-slate-700 text-xs border border-slate-300">Collective Intelligence</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-slate-200">
          <div class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-2">Key Research Areas:</div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 text-xs">
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
              <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-slate-400"></div>
              <span class="text-slate-600">Scalable multi-agent coordination algorithms</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
              <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-slate-500"></div>
              <span class="text-slate-600">Open-world task decomposition and planning</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
              <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-slate-400"></div>
              <span class="text-slate-600">Social intelligence in large communities</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
        <!-- Community Robot Challenge -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-slate-100 border border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center mr-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-slate-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Community Robot</h3>
            <div class="text-slate-600 text-sm font-semibold">Physically Realistic Multi-Robot Cooperation</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Robots cooperate to complete complex tasks spanning both indoor and dynamic open-world environments, 
          leveraging physically realistic simulations powered by the Genesis engine.
        </p>
          <div class="space-y-6">
          <!-- Physical Realism -->
          <div class="bg-slate-50 p-4 border border-slate-200">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-slate-100 border border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13.828 10.172a4 4 0 00-5.656 0l-4 4a4 4 0 105.656 5.656l1.102-1.101m-.758-4.899a4 4 0 005.656 0l4-4a4 4 0 00-5.656-5.656l-1.1 1.1"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Genesis Physics Engine</h4>
            </div>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-3">
              Realistic physics simulation enables complex robot-robot and robot-environment interactions.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-slate-200 text-slate-700 text-xs border border-slate-300">Collision Detection</span>
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-slate-200 text-slate-700 text-xs border border-slate-300">Force Dynamics</span>
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-slate-200 text-slate-700 text-xs border border-slate-300">Material Properties</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Multi-Environment Tasks -->
          <div class="bg-slate-50 p-4 border border-slate-200">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-slate-100 border border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Cross-Environment Coordination</h4>
            </div>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-3">
              Tasks that span both indoor spaces and dynamic outdoor environments with traffic and crowds.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-slate-200 text-slate-700 text-xs border border-slate-300">Indoor Navigation</span>
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-slate-200 text-slate-700 text-xs border border-slate-300">Outdoor Mobility</span>
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-slate-200 text-slate-700 text-xs border border-slate-300">Dynamic Environments</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-slate-200">
          <div class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-2">Research Opportunities:</div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 text-xs">
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
              <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-slate-400"></div>
              <span class="text-slate-600">Multi-robot task allocation and coordination</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
              <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-slate-500"></div>
              <span class="text-slate-600">Physics-aware planning and control</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
              <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-slate-400"></div>
              <span class="text-slate-600">Real-world transfer learning</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
      <!-- Impact Statement -->
    <div class="mt-16 bg-slate-50 p-8 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Advancing Embodied General Intelligence</h3>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          By overcoming limitations in scalable, realistic open-world scene generation and community simulation, 
          Virtual Community paves the way for studying <span class="text-slate-900 font-semibold">embodied general intelligence</span> 
          in environments that reflect the <span class="text-slate-900 font-semibold">complexity and richness of the real world</span>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
